OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772737887
OL,3,CHMS Dragon will not sail until next
OL,4,Cweek, as Starmer defends position on
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FThe HMS Dragon - the warship being
OL,8,Freadied to protect the British base in
OL,9,FCyprus - is not set to sail until next
OL,10,Fweek, as the conflict in the Middle
OL,11,FEast continues to escalate.
OL,13,FThe Royal Navy destroyer is being
OL,14,Floaded with ammunition in Portsmouth,
OL,15,Fbefore it departs for the
OL,16,FMediterranean.
OL,18,FThe announcement that the UK would
OL,19,Fsend the warship came on Tuesday after
OL,20,Fthe RAF Akrotiri was hit by a drone in
OL,21,Fthe early hours of Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772737887
OL,3,CHMS Dragon will not sail until next
OL,4,Cweek, as Starmer defends position on
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FOfficials said there was nothing that
OL,8,Fwould have happened to ready a warship
OL,9,Fany earlier, amid questions over
OL,10,FBritain's preparedness to protect its
OL,11,Fbases overseas.
OL,13,FThey would not specify where the drone
OL,14,Fwhich struck Akrotiri had come from,
OL,15,Fbut said assessments showed it was a
OL,16,FShahed type and had not been launched
OL,17,Ffrom Iran.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
