FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772737887
OL,3,CHMS Dragon will not sail until next
OL,4,Cweek, as Starmer defends position on
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FAsked by journalists why there was no
OL,8,FType 45 destroyer sent to the region
OL,9,Fmonths ago during a US military build-
OL,10,Fup, they said increasingly fragile
OL,11,Fgeopolitics with many different
OL,12,Fsecurity threats made the situation
OL,13,Fcomplex.
OL,15,FHMS Dragon was chosen because it was
OL,16,Fthe readiest for the mission,
OL,17,Fofficials said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
