PN,31904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772737887
OL,3,CHMS Dragon will not sail until next
OL,4,Cweek, as Starmer defends position on
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FMeanwhile, Royal Navy Wildcat
OL,8,Fhelicopters armed with Martlet drone-
OL,9,Fbusting missiles are being deployed
OL,10,Fwithin days, before the warship, to
OL,11,Fbolster defence in the region, they
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,FThe Type 45 air defence destroyer is
OL,15,Fintended to strengthen protection
OL,16,Fagainst drones and missiles launched
OL,17,Fby Iran and its proxies such as
OL,18,FHezbollah in Lebanon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
