OL,3,CHMS Dragon will not sail until next
OL,4,Cweek, as Starmer defends position on
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FThe destroyer's voyage from Portsmouth
OL,8,Fto Cyprus is expected to take several
OL,9,Fdays.
OL,11,FThe latest development comes after
OL,12,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer was
OL,13,Fforced to defend his position, and
OL,14,FPresident Trump's response to it,
OL,15,Fduring Prime Minister's Questions on
OL,16,FWednesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
