PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772737887
OL,3,CHMS Dragon will not sail until next
OL,4,Cweek, as Starmer defends position on
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FHe argued that "hanging onto Trump's
OL,8,Flatest words is not the special
OL,9,Frelationship in action" after Trump's
OL,10,Flatest attack on the prime minister
OL,11,Fover his response to the war in Iran.
OL,13,FStarmer was asked if his "dithering
OL,14,Fand equivocal response" to events in
OL,15,Fthe Middle East had improved the
OL,16,Frelationship with the US.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772737887
OL,3,CHMS Dragon will not sail until next
OL,4,Cweek, as Starmer defends position on
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,F"American planes are operating out of
OL,8,FBritish bases. That is the special
OL,9,Frelationship in action... Hanging on
OL,10,Fto President Trump's latest words is
OL,11,Fnot the special relationship in
OL,12,Faction," the PM told the Commons.
OL,14,FHe said the crisis in the Middle East
OL,15,Frequired a "cool head" as he defended
OL,16,Fhis response to the situation and that
OL,17,Fhis priority was the safety of the
OL,18,FBritish people.
OL,26,@wD@LOUwD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
