OL,3,CHMS Dragon will not sail until next
OL,4,Cweek, as Starmer defends position on
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FSpeaking in the Oval Office on Tuesday
OL,8,Fduring a visit from the German
OL,9,FChancellor, President Trump said he is
OL,10,F"not happy" with the UK and with
OL,11,FStarmer, and that "this is not Winston
OL,12,FChurchill that we're dealing with".
OL,14,FTrump's comments referred to Starmer's
OL,15,Fdecision not to be involved in the
OL,16,Finitial US strikes on Iran, despite
OL,17,Flater deciding to allow the use of
OL,18,FBritish bases for "defensive" strikes
OL,19,Fon Iranian missile sites to protect
OL,20,Fcountries being targeted by Tehran.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@KO]sD@SOUtD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
