PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772737887
OL,3,CHMS Dragon will not sail until next
OL,4,Cweek, as Starmer defends position on
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FDuring PMQs, Tory leader Kemi Badenoch
OL,8,Fasked why the RAF had not taken
OL,9,F"offensive action" to destroy Iranian
OL,10,Fmissile sites after British bases in
OL,11,FBahrain and Cyprus had been attacked.
OL,13,FStarmer replied: "The protection of UK
OL,14,Fnationals is our number one priority.
OL,15,FWe're taking action to reduce the
OL,16,Fthreat with planes in the sky in the
OL,17,Fregion intercepting incoming strikes,
OL,18,Fdeploying more capability to Cyprus,
OL,19,Fand allowing US planes to use UK bases
OL,20,Fto take out Iran's capability to
OL,21,Fstrike."
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@RO]uD@ROU}D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
