PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772737887
OL,3,CHMS Dragon will not sail until next
OL,4,Cweek, as Starmer defends position on
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,F"This government will be resolute in
OL,8,Four focus, protecting British lives,
OL,9,Fbringing our people home, and
OL,10,Fsafeguarding our national interest,"
OL,11,Fthe prime minister said.
OL,13,FStarmer has sought to limit UK
OL,14,Finvolvement in the war, but decided on
OL,15,FSunday that the joint British-US Diego
OL,16,FGarcia site in the Chagos Islands and
OL,17,FRAF Fairford in Gloucestershire could
OL,18,Fbe used defensively by the US.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
