CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772737887
OL,3,CHMS Dragon will not sail until next
OL,4,Cweek, as Starmer defends position on
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,FHMS Dragon, one of the Royal Navy's
OL,8,Fsix Type 45 air defence destroyers, is
OL,9,Fbeing readied to depart for the
OL,10,FMediterranean to defend Cyprus after
OL,11,FRAF Akrotiri was hit by a drone.
OL,13,FIn response to the destroyer's delayed
OL,14,Fdeployment, a Ministry of Defence
OL,15,Fspokesperson said: "We are reinforcing
OL,16,Four defensive presence in the Eastern
OL,17,FMediterranean. Royal Navy Wildcat
OL,18,Fhelicopters armed with Martlet drone-
OL,19,Fbusting missiles are deploying within
OL,20,Fdays.
OL,26,@wD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31912
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1772737887
OL,3,CHMS Dragon will not sail until next
OL,4,Cweek, as Starmer defends position on
OL,5,CIran
OL,7,F"They will reinforce our RAF Typhoons,
OL,8,FF-35B jets, ground-based counter-drone
OL,9,Fteams, radar systems, and Voyager
OL,10,Frefuelling aircraft already deployed.
OL,11,FOur jets are now flying continuous
OL,12,Fsorties to defend against
OL,13,Findiscriminate Iranian strikes
OL,14,Fthreatening UK people, interests, and
OL,15,Fbases.
OL,17,F"The Royal Navy are working as fast as
OL,18,Fpossible to prepare HMS Dragon for
OL,19,Fdeployment, including resupplying her
OL,20,Fair defence missiles at our ammunition
OL,21,Ffacility in HMNB in Portsmouth."
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@AOU}D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/13
